"SELLER IS OFFERING INTEREST RATE BUY DOWN WITH AN ACCEPTED OFFER!"
Beautiful home nestled among live oaks and sits on 1.5 acres! Bright and inviting; Large living area with stoned fireplace and built-in shelving on each side; Spacious kitchen with stainless steel appliances; Large kitchen island and breakfast bar has plenty of room to cook and visit with guests; Built-in microwave and beverage fridge;Open concept living, dining and kitchen;Large laundry/pantry room off the kitchen;Master and one other bedroom have an ensuite; Walk-in showers; Sitting area and walk-in closet off the master bedroom;Multi-level decks in the fenced-in backyard to relax and have a cookout on;Smart thermostats; Ring doorbell;Storage Building;RV Hookup; MAKE THIS YOUR NEW HOME OR INVESTMENT PROPERTY!Great Airbnb or VRBO opportunity!Less than 5 miles from the river and Zedler Mill Park & Pavilion Venue!Close to Luling, San Marcos, SH 130 and easy commute to Austin and San Antonio!Large screen television in the living area, refrigerator, washer, and dryer convey with sale.
